channel.title: Dds-speced 525
channel.description:
[center]Hello,Previously my server 'dds-speced 525' was growing faster than alot of most 525's.
if you can remember you would of seen it on the toplist.
Within a week and a half we were rank 10 on runelocus toplist.
From now today we are coding dds-speced 525 back with alot of features set out to be the most advanced 525 out.
[b]Features :[/b]
[code]
-Bounty hunter
-castle wars 80%
-Perfect Pvp combat
-95% specials
-perfect special times
-New started equiptment
-Lumbridge is home once again.
-250+ Pvp drops
-20% shops
-Anti Spam
-Dragon claws are rare
-banking
-Mage Bank
-Friend list receive/Send.
-Trading 85% (because no trade limit)
[/code]
[b] Coming soon :[/b]
[code]
-100% Shops
-100% Kbd
-100% Kq
-100% castle wars
-100% clan wars
-Barrows
-Non-pvp
-wildy 100%
-100% no lag.
[/code]
dds-speced 525 was created so all the player,
and staff can have a really good time.
We are currently still constructing legacy 525 so it wont be released soon.
this project thread will keep you updated on dds-speced 525
and tell you all the new features.
[b] Staff :[/b]
[b] Owners :[/b]
Dds-Pker (Me Legacy508) [b]
Admins :[/b]
Open
Open
Open
[b]mods[/b] Open
Open
Open
[b] Pvp And Pvn[/b]
we have perfect Pvp and almost perfect Pvn.
I worked really hard on this for the upcomming Kq,kbd Ect.
We will need it to be perfect also if you want a really great server.
[b] Lag issues[/b]
dds-speced 525 will have lag when it is finished but i am working on alot
of anti-lag soloutions to help this..
We will want this server to be most advanced so if we want players
there server shouldnt have lag because players hate lag am i right?
[b] Drops[/b]
Dds-speced 525 has many drops and i mean many.
over 250 drops.
the rarest drops to get i would say are
[code]
D claws
Ags
Zgs
Bandos peices
D pl8
and statuis items
[/code]
[b] NEW UPDATES :[/b]
[code]
Drops are more rare for good items.
Godsword shards make godswords 45%
20% on our new costum 525 client
[/code][/center]
